data.description: Two-bedroom, two-bath ranch home on a nicely landscaped 1/2 acre lot.  Almost 1,500 sq ft completely updated. Open concept living area creates a welcoming feeling. Living room is tucked in and cozy.  Kitchen has lots of cabinets and counter space and tasteful vinyl plank flooring. Master bedroom has a huge ensuite bath with a large jetted whirlpool tub and a large closet.  Beautiful hardwood floors throughout.  Some very nice hardwood accent walls.  Large laundry /storage area.  Two-car detached garage with room for cabinets and workbench.  2 storage sheds.  House has an insulated crawl space and newly added attic insulation. New roof in 2015.  Siding replaced in 2015.  New Furnace and air conditioner in 2019.  New inside doors, ceiling fans and paint throughout  This home is move-in ready and attention to detail is evident throughout.  The Vivint alarm system worth over $2,000 will be left. All kitchen appliances are less than 2 years old and will be staying.
